dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for Waushara County, Wisconsin in 2020. [This data set was developed initially automated by the WI Department of Natural Resources. It is updated and on an on going basis, by Waushara County. The data contained in this file only covers points address information managed by the County.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: [https://waushara.maps.arcgis.com/home/index.html]
